1944;;Goodnight, Sweetheart;;American;;Joseph Santley;;Robert Livingston, Ruth Terry, Henry Hull;;musical comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Goodnight,_Sweetheart_(1944_film);;Goodnight, Sweetheart is a comedy that includes a couple's offbeat romance. Mainly, a reporter takes on the mayoral race of a candidate that has been endorsed by a rival newspaper.[4]